'''外周循环肿瘤细胞'''，（Circulating Tumor Cell，简称CTC），是脱落到[[血管|血管]]或[[淋巴管|淋巴管]]系统中的[[贅生物|腫瘤]]細胞<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Riquet |first=M |last2=Rivera |first2=C |last3=Gibault |first3=L |last4=Pricopi |first4=C |last5=Mordant |first5=P |last6=Badia |first6=A |last7=Arame |first7=A |last8=Le Pimpec Barthes |first8=F |year=2014 |title=[Lymphatic spread of lung cancer: anatomical lymph node chains unchained in zones] |journal=Revue de Pneumologie Clinique |volume=70 |issue=1–2 |page=16–25 |doi=10.1016/j.pneumo.2013.07.001 |pmid=24566031}}</ref>， 因其藉由血液循環擴散到其他器官，進而形成腫瘤[[遠端轉移|遠端轉移]]的能力，常被稱為轉移癌的「種子」(seeds)。 <ref>{{Cite journal |last=Gupta |first=GP |last2=Massagué, J |date=Nov 17, 2006 |title=Cancer metastasis: building a framework |journal=Cell |volume=127 |issue=4 |page=679–95 |doi=10.1016/j.cell.2006.11.001 |pmid=17110329 |s2cid=7362869 |doi-access=free}}</ref> CTC的檢測與分析可以協助癌症早期診斷及個人化療法的選擇 <ref name="Rack">{{Cite journal |vauthors=Rack B, Schindlbeck C, Jückstock J, Andergassen U, Hepp P, Zwingers T, Friedl T, Lorenz R, Tesch H, Fasching P, Fehm T, Schneeweiss A, Lichtenegger W, Beckmann M, Friese K, Pantel K, Janni W |year=2014 |title=Circulating Tumor Cells Predict Survival in Early Average-to-High Risk Breast Cancer Patients |journal=Journal of the National Cancer Institute |volume=106 |issue=5 |doi=10.1093/jnci/dju066 |pmc=4112925 |pmid=24832787}}</ref>，其中一種名為CellSearch的方法在[[乳癌|乳腺癌]]、[[大腸癌|结肠直肠癌]]和[[前列腺癌|前列腺]]癌的診斷上已受[[美國食品藥物管理局|美國食品藥物管理局]]核可。 <ref>{{Cite journal |last=Millner |first=LM |last2=Linder |first2=MW |last3=Valdes R |first3=Jr |date=Summer 2013 |title=Circulating tumor cells: a review of present methods and the need to identify heterogeneous phenotypes. |journal=Annals of Clinical and Laboratory Science |volume=43 |issue=3 |page=295–304 |pmc=5060940 |pmid=23884225}}</ref>
